Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:02.87,中文,,0,0,0,,【吸血鬼日记】 前情提要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Previously on "The Vampire Diaries"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.87,0:00:04.29,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damon's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:06.04,中文,,0,0,0,,阿拉里克能抹去我所有的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Alaric will compel away any memories
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.92,中文,,0,0,0,,关于达蒙和我在一起的记忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I had of Damon and me being together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.12,中文,,0,0,0,,泰勒和斯特凡已经走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tyler and Stefan are on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:11.32,中文,,0,0,0,,抹除吧 求你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just take it away, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:13.30,中文,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼不能进入神秘瀑布镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Vampires can't get into Mystic Falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.48,中文,,0,0,0,,-他们能在边境埋伏 -啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- They can lurk around the borders. - Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:16.89,中文,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:18.89,中文,,0,0,0,,卡罗琳让她忘记埃琳娜攻击了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Caroline compelled her to forget Elena attacked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:20.03,中文,,0,0,0,,没有什么大不了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:21.30,中文,,0,0,0,,你来自神秘瀑布镇么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're from Mystic Falls?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.70,中文,,0,0,0,,事实上是来自其中一个创始人家族\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}One of the founding families actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:24.13,中文,,0,0,0,,有遗言吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Any final words?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:26.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我们到底在哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where the hell are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:27.74,中文,,0,0,0,,1994\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}1994.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:29.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我们通过魔法来到的这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We got here by magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:30.54,中文,,0,0,0,,魔法应该能把我们带离这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Magic should be able to get us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:31.81,中文,,0,0,0,,看看谁填了横27行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look who got 27 across.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:34.14,中文,,0,0,0,,-我没完成这个 -我也没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I didn't finish this. - Well, neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:36.28,中文,,0,0,0,,有别的人在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's someone else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:37.92,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡没有告别\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stefan didn't say good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:40.56,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙和邦妮死了 而他就这么走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damon and Bonnie died, and he just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:41.60,中文,,0,0,0,,放开她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:55.96,中文,,0,0,0,,这儿不是停车场 孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ain't a parking lot, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:57.60,中文,,0,0,0,,是么 嗯 我不是来这儿工作的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah? Well, I'm not here to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:00:58.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我要请假\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Need a few days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:01.18,中文,,0,0,0,,看来我需要新的工作机器了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And it looks like I need a new mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:06.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我说我需要休息几天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I said I need a few days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:08.01,中文,,0,0,0,,你反应迟钝么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:09.14,中文,,0,0,0,,简单来说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let me simplify.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.14,0:01:12.55,中文,,0,0,0,,留下来 有工作 请假 就直接下岗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stay... keep the job. Leave... lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:15.42,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:17.55,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这么有力气\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How the hell are you so strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你雇了个吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You hired a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:21.06,中文,,0,0,0,,下次 记得调查员工背景\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Next time, do a background check.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:23.86,中文,,0,0,0,,现在闭嘴 别动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now shut up and don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:28.23,中文,,0,0,0,,你不知道我想这么做多久了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You have no idea how long I've wanted to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:30.36,中文,,0,0,0,,你看 我想要一个全新的开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}See, I was trying to get a fresh start,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:35.44,中文,,0,0,0,,有正常的生活 正常的工作 正常的混蛋老板\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}live a normal life, normal job, normal dick of a boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:36.80,中文,,0,0,0,,这个说的就是你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's you by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.81,0:01:38.84,中文,,0,0,0,,这个地方应该是我的庇护所\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This place was supposed to be my sanctuary,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:42.11,中文,,0,0,0,,直到昨天一直是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and it was until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:43.54,中文,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:51.99,中文,,0,0,0,,那是我的女朋友艾薇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's my girlfriend Ivy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.99,0:01:54.12,中文,,0,0,0,,昨天晚上有人就在我眼前杀了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Somebody killed her last night right in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:56.16,中文,,0,0,0,,所以现在我要回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so now I need to go back home...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:58.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我最不想去的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Last place on this planet I want to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:00.63,中文,,0,0,0,,找到他 然后杀了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Find him, and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:05.73,中文,,0,0,0,,像我说过的 我需要请假\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Like I said, I need a few days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:07.57,中文,,0,0,0,,你应该需要休假了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You should take a few days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:10.07,中文,,0,0,0,,谢了 伙计 我会的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thanks, buddy. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:12.77,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我要你开着我的车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now I need you to drive my car
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.41,中文,,0,0,0,,进树林里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}into the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:17.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你要埋了我的女友 然后忘掉发生的这一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're gonna bury my girlfriend and forget this ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:21.31,中文,,0,0,0,,哦对了 我回来之后 你要给我加薪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, and when I get back, you're giving me a raise.
