Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.12,中文,,0,0,0,,所以 我 嗯 自愿在医院呆到 比如说 两点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So I, uh, volunteer at the hospital until, like, 2:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:43.09,中文,,0,0,0,,之后 我觉得我们可以拼车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and then I figure we can carpool
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:45.56,中文,,0,0,0,,去深水湖的派对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to the party at the swimming hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.77,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 一般你搬回来的时候会拿出你的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Um, normally when you move back in, you unpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我不打算留在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:55.10,中文,,0,0,0,,昨晚只是一时的懦弱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Last night was just a momentary moment of weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.97,中文,,0,0,0,,一时的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Momentary moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:03:00.38,中文,,0,0,0,,你确定你不想回学校么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you sure you don't want to come back to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:03.61,中文,,0,0,0,,卡罗琳 需要朋友并不代表着懦弱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Caroline, needing your friends isn't a weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:06.55,中文,,0,0,0,,一时的 或是别的什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}momentary or otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:10.85,中文,,0,0,0,,对斯特凡去讲 他显然谁也不需要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tell that to Stefan, who clearly needs no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:14.29,中文,,0,0,0,,给他点空间吧 他失去了哥哥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Cut him some slack. He lost his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.46,中文,,0,0,0,,的确 他哥哥是没有灵魂的杀人狂魔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Granted, said brother was a soulless homicidal maniac,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.96,中文,,0,0,0,,但是血浓于水\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but still.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.83,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.90,中文,,0,0,0,,没什么 只是 只是我得走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nothing. I just... I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:27.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我要和恩佐去吃早饭 所以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've got breakfast with Enzo, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.77,中文,,0,0,0,,-恩佐么 -对啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Enzo? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你们一起去旅行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You guys go on one road trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:33.24,中文,,0,0,0,,突然之间 你们一起去吃早饭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and all of a sudden, you're breakfast buddies?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.71,中文,,0,0,0,,对啊 我是这么想的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.48,中文,,0,0,0,,讽刺的是 他的确已经成为了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ironically, he's recently become
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我生活中最安稳的一个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}one of the more stable people in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:42.91,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 邀请他去派对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok. Then invite him to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.79,中文,,0,0,0,,-埃琳娜 -拜托 我有马特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Elena. - Come on. I got Matt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:48.06,中文,,0,0,0,,不让他进行下午的训练\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to take the afternoon off from his training
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:50.16,中文,,0,0,0,,泰勒也要暂停球队练习\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and Tyler to give the practice squad a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.39,中文,,0,0,0,,连杰里米也会来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Even Jeremy is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我们真的好久没有在一起过了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's been forever since we've all been together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.70,中文,,0,0,0,,会很有趣的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:04:00.23,中文,,0,0,0,,别让我用核武器的强硬方式\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't make me invoke the nuclear option.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:03.40,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我会每隔五分钟轰炸你一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because I will selfie bomb you every 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:07.48,中文,,0,0,0,,-好吧 我会去派对的 -太棒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Ok. Fine. I'll go to the party. - Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.54,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我不会搬过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I'm not moving back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:13.61,中文,,0,0,0,,那个对话应该在拍广告的时候讲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That is a conversation to be had over jell-o shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.46,中文,,0,0,0,,阿拉里克对她做了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What did Alaric do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道她不记得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All I know is she doesn't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:21.16,中文,,0,0,0,,她看到了达蒙的什么事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}whatever it is she saw in Damon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:22.65,中文,,0,0,0,,并且我们应该让过去成为过去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and we're supposed to keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我刚刚和她度过了一整晚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I just spent the whole night with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:26.12,中文,,0,0,0,,感觉很奇怪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and it's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.99,中文,,0,0,0,,她一点也不像原来的样子了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She just doesn't seem like her old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.55,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 那是因为她很快乐 这不就是关键么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. It's because she's happy. Isn't that the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我想是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:34.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我得挂了 之后再联系\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look. I got to go. I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:36.03,中文,,0,0,0,,现在洗车还太早吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's a little early for a carwash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:37.83,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 我买了一些护根\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, yeah. I brought in some mulch
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:40.13,中文,,0,0,0,,好让你们去清理四号那个小公园\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so you guys could clean up that little park on 4th.
