Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:25.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是很高兴终于见到你了 你知道吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm just happy to finally see you again, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:30.88,中文,,0,0,0,,这几个月以来 失去邦妮真的是让人很难熬\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's been really rough losing Bonnie the last couple of months...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.99,中文,,0,0,0,,对着一个失去哥哥的人来说这事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Which is an incredibly insensitive thing to say
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.50,中文,,0,0,0,,也太不合适了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to somebody who just lost their brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:39.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我 对不起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:42.37,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我也一直在试着从中走出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. I've been working on the healing thing, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我想是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:47.91,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 额 顺便问一句 你有卡罗琳的消息吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey. Uh, by the way, have you, uh, heard from Caroline?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.41,中文,,0,0,0,,她没有回复我的电话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's not returning any of my calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:53.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我真的很想为我的表现道个歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I really want to apologize for the way I acted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.05,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 今天她会在深水湖那边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, she'll be there at the swimming hole today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.42,中文,,0,0,0,,你应该来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You should come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.49,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不 我还不确定我是否准备好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, no. I'm not sure I'm ready to dive
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.85,中文,,0,0,0,,又跳回到那堆东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}back into all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我没有双重意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No pun intended.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:06.16,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡 他们也是你的朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stefan, they're your friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.86,中文,,0,0,0,,来吧 我知道我们不能像以前在酒吧那样一起玩乐了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on. I know that we can't hang out at the grill anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.86,中文,,0,0,0,,但那并不意味着我们不能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but that doesn't mean we can't all spend
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:12.70,中文,,0,0,0,,一起打发时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.50,中文,,0,0,0,,来吧 拜托了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:17.27,中文,,0,0,0,,如果不是为了那样 那么至少去说服卡罗琳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If not for that, then at least to convince Caroline that Enzo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:20.57,中文,,0,0,0,,恩佐不是新的好朋友的候选人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is not new best friend replacement material.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.98,中文,,0,0,0,,恩佐也会在那\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Will Enzo be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:26.05,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 但我很轻易就能把他踢走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, but I can easily uninvite him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:28.21,中文,,0,0,0,,-我更想你来 -不 不用担心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I'd rather you come. - No. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.12,中文,,0,0,0,,额\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:34.95,中文,,0,0,0,,-好吧 也许我会去看看 -很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Yeah. Maybe I'll stop by. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.89,中文,,0,0,0,,你了解规则了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you understand the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.89,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 规则一 不要提起埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. Rule one... Don't mention Elena
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:42.36,中文,,0,0,0,,曾经疯狂地爱着达蒙 不然你会杀了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}was madly in love with Damon, or you'll kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.50,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:44.68,中文,,0,0,0,,规则二 一点也不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rule two... don't really
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.77,中文,,0,0,0,,谈到达蒙 不然你会杀了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}reference Damon at all, or you'll kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:47.87,中文,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:52.34,中文,,0,0,0,,-规则三 搽防晒霜 -别拿我开玩笑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Rule 3... wear sunscreen... - Don't make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:56.21,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要让埃琳娜过着她想要的 新的快乐的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's important that we let Elena live her new happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:59.88,中文,,0,0,0,,无视问题的僵尸生活 这很重要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}problem-ignoring zombie life the way she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:04.45,中文,,0,0,0,,这真是一句听起来又支持又有意见的奇怪句子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A sentence which sounded oddly supportive and judgmental.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我支持她 她做了她需要做的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I support her. She did what she needed to do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:10.36,中文,,0,0,0,,去停止撕咬无辜路人的行为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to stop chomping on innocent people on the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:11.86,中文,,0,0,0,,但这不等于我享受\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but it doesn't mean that I'm enjoying
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:14.49,中文,,0,0,0,,独自泡在痛苦的感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}marinating all alone in my misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:17.28,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我和你一起泡着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, I'll marinate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:22.23,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你这句话 真的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I appreciate it. Really, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.84,中文,,0,0,0,,但我不是斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I'm not Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:28.24,中文,,0,0,0,,规则四 不要再提起那个混蛋的名字 不然\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rule number 4... don't ever mention that jerk's name again, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:31.58,中文,,0,0,0,,不然你会杀了我 我明白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Or you'll kill me. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:35.05,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦 那是血还是派的污渍\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Whoa! Is that blood or pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.11,中文,,0,0,0,,请你告诉我是派\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Please say pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:39.55,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 那是 额\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh. That would be, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:42.35,中文,,0,0,0,,雪莉 一个菜单上没有的特别菜品\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shirley, a special off-the-menu item.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.39,中文,,0,0,0,,这顿小晚餐的味道保持得真好啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This little diner is surprisingly well-stocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:48.53,中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我你已经抢来了 吃了 擦除记忆了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tell me that you snatched, ate, erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:49.76,中文,,0,0,0,,那真是有趣的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Funny thing about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你很好地做了前两件事 第三件事就不必要了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You do the first two properly, the third isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.98,中文,,0,0,0,,-你杀了她吗 -哦 别表现得那么惊讶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You killed her? - Oh, don't act all shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:56.53,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 不好意思 死亡总是让我很惊讶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, I'm sorry, but death shocks me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.58,中文,,0,0,0,,而且还会带来一份失踪人口报告\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and it also leads to a missing persons report,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:00.77,中文,,0,0,0,,-然后又带来 -警官的调查吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- which leads to... - A sheriff's investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:01.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我好怕怕哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我已经被警告三次了 再有一次 就有惩罚了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I already have 3 warnings. One more, it's a fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:14.09,中文,,0,0,0,,这里应该会有一条短的错误的电线之类的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's got to be a short, faulty wiring, something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:18.12,中文,,0,0,0,,或者是有人放了一个硬币进去就打开了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Or someone put a quarter in it and turned it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:23.19,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我对这些寄托错地方的希望有些疑惑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know, I'm a little confused with all this misplaced hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:26.26,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 就说有人在这吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right. Let's just say there's someone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:28.43,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我们会出的去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How do you know we're gonna get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:31.14,中文,,0,0,0,,你说过这就是你的地狱 对吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, you say that this is your hell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:34.41,中文,,0,0,0,,如果有其他人在这 那就表明这不是你的地狱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If there's someone else here, that means it's not your hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.34,中文,,0,0,0,,如果这不是你的地狱 那就表明是外婆放我们到这的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and if it's not your hell, that means grams put us here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:39.78,中文,,0,0,0,,如果是外婆放我们到这的 那就会有出去的路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and if grams put us here, there's a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.95,中文,,0,0,0,,那只是你自己绕进去的一套逻辑怪圈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's a hell of a logic knot you've tied for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.85,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢 所以现在我们已经\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thank you. So now that we've
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.98,中文,,0,0,0,,放置好我们的希望 开始玩游戏吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}properly placed our hope, let's play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.22,中文,,0,0,0,,当我们出了去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When we get out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:54.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你会首先和埃琳娜说什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}what's the first thing you're gonna tell Elena?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.53,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉我杀死了邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry I killed Bonnie,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.66,中文,,0,0,0,,但她是世上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but she was the most annoying person
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:00.33,中文,,0,0,0,,最讨人烦的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:03.13,中文,,0,0,0,,她关不上她的嘴 话说个不停\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She wouldn't shut up. She just kept talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我是说 只要我杀了邦妮那我就创造了一个奇迹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, it's a wonder I made it as long as I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.64,中文,,0,0,0,,但是事情是这样子的 我觉得这样更好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but here's the thing. I think it's better this way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:09.67,中文,,0,0,0,,因为她没有了魔法 并且她一无是处\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because she didn't have magic, and she was pretty much useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.82,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙 怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Damon. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:15.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道 你仍然觉得我一无是处\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know. You still think I'm useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:21.82,中文,,0,0,0,,那不是我的车么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:25.19,中文,,0,0,0,,那就是我的车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's my car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:28.66,中文,,0,0,0,,她是个坚定的人但是很甜美\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's determined but sweet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:32.23,中文,,0,0,0,,是个永恒的乐天派 从不忘记生日\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}eternal optimist, never forgets a birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.53,中文,,0,0,0,,还有其它的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:36.40,中文,,0,0,0,,从不放弃她的朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Never gives up on her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:39.24,中文,,0,0,0,,没错 她非常的忠心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes. True. She's completely loyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:41.21,中文,,0,0,0,,不错啊  你们这么捧她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is good. Build her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:44.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我确定她会活在那些荒唐的很高的期望中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sure she'll live up to these ridiculously high expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:45.48,中文,,0,0,0,,还有一个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.41,中文,,0,0,0,,那就是她善于超出所有的期望\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Great at surpassing expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:49.85,中文,,0,0,0,,那她很完美啊 完完全全地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- So she's perfect. - Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.68,中文,,0,0,0,,几乎完美\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.38,中文,,0,0,0,,那么你们俩在一起多久了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So how long have you two been together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:56.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我们 不 我们只是 额\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Us? No. I'm... we're... heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:59.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我们没在一起 我是说 过去我们确实在一起过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're not, but, I mean, we did at one point...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.96,中文,,0,0,0,,再也回不去咯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.26,中文,,0,0,0,,是最近分的手么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Was that recent?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:04.43,中文,,0,0,0,,因为你们俩看起来怪怪的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because you two seem weirdly functional.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:07.03,中文,,0,0,0,,已经过去两年了吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Has it already been two years?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:11.80,中文,,0,0,0,,岁月如梭啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Time flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.40,中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:18.98,中文,,0,0,0,,我们还要听你呜呜多久啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How much longer are we gonna listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.94,中文,,0,0,0,,嘘 别出声\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shh, shh, shh, shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:23.45,中文,,0,0,0,,这声音比你的嗓音好听不知多少\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This sound is the opposite sound of your voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.55,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我很喜欢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I so enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:29.75,中文,,0,0,0,,这辆车怎么会在这里的 达蒙 是你在1994年把它留在这的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How did it even get here, Damon? Did you leave it here in 1994?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:32.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道 邦妮 那是18年前的事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know, Bonnie. It was 18 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.19,中文,,0,0,0,,那天我可是很忙的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Has a lot going on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:37.93,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 所以你就承认这不大可能是你留下的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok. So you admit that it's pretty unlikely that you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.43,中文,,0,0,0,,非常不可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Very unlikely.
