Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:48.78,中文,,0,0,0,,所有你真的觉得自己死定了 没有希望了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so if you're really done, if you have none,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:50.92,中文,,0,0,0,,那就去死吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}then be done
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:53.05,中文,,0,0,0,,在这抱怨根本没用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because this isn't helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:28.25,中文,,0,0,0,,真是艰难的一天 是不是 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rough day, huh, Damon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:31.39,中文,,0,0,0,,不好意思 忘记了礼数 我是凯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry. Manners. I'm Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:33.13,中文,,0,0,0,,见到你很高兴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.13,0:23:34.73,中文,,0,0,0,,吃猪皮吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pork rind?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:47.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你确定你能找到回家的路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you're sure you're ok to find your way back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:48.98,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我的朋友卡罗琳她最近\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry. My friend Caroline's having
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.98,0:23:50.75,中文,,0,0,0,,有一些麻烦缠身\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a bit of a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:53.09,中文,,0,0,0,,这几个月对她来说很难过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's been a rough couple of months for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:55.16,中文,,0,0,0,,她平常很好人的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's normally really sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.16,0:23:57.08,中文,,0,0,0,,说真的 我很庆幸没见到她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Actually, I'm glad I didn't meet her
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:23:58.63,中文,,0,0,0,,要不然我这么做的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because then it would have been awkward
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.63,0:24:00.29,中文,,0,0,0,,就会很尴尬了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}when I did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:10.86,中文,,0,0,0,,亲一个为你和\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Heh. Kissing a girl who's
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.86,0:24:13.54,中文,,0,0,0,,闺蜜搭线的女生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}trying to set you up with her best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.54,0:24:15.58,中文,,0,0,0,,这样做不是很好哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Red flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.58,0:24:17.35,中文,,0,0,0,,也许吧 我感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe. I have a sneaking suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:19.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我是你喜欢的类型\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that's your type.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.60,0:24:40.10,中文,,0,0,0,,这些冰是给卡罗琳的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That was Caroline's ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.10,0:24:41.50,中文,,0,0,0,,是嘛 反正你都要死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. Well, you'll be dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.50,0:24:44.31,中文,,0,0,0,,她应该不会怪你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so I think she'll let you off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.11,0:24:50.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我不想杀你 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't want to kill you, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.91,0:24:53.45,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Unh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.52,0:25:01.79,中文,,0,0,0,,但是他似乎是想的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But it looks like he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.23,0:25:16.90,中文,,0,0,0,,我以为我叫了恩佐去拿冰来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I thought I told Enzo to go get more ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.91,0:25:18.67,中文,,0,0,0,,你就是用这种语气跟他说的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did you do it in that tone?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.67,0:25:20.97,中文,,0,0,0,,那我知道他为什么没有了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because I think I know why he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.98,0:25:23.58,中文,,0,0,0,,恭喜你 现在这是你的事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Congratulations. Now it's your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.58,0:25:25.69,中文,,0,0,0,,去拿些冰来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go get ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.31,0:25:29.61,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不是来找乐子的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aren't we supposed to be having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.23,0:25:32.73,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你把你最新泡上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that why you brought your latest fling
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.73,0:25:34.20,中文,,0,0,0,,的妹子带到这来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in a series of sad attempts
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.20,0:25:35.96,中文,,0,0,0,,假装你已经忘了邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to pretend like you don't care about Bonnie...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.96,0:25:38.14,中文,,0,0,0,,来找乐子吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.14,0:25:44.31,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 后援来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Right. Cavalry's on their way,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.31,0:25:47.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我们暂停一下小打小闹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so why don't we put a pin in our little spat
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.08,0:25:49.45,中文,,0,0,0,,把这个解决了再继续怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}till this all gets sorted, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.85,0:25:52.28,中文,,0,0,0,,不用了 谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.29,0:25:53.82,中文,,0,0,0,,你特么肯定是在逗我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You've got to be bloody kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.82,0:25:55.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我刚刚救了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I just saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.26,0:25:57.32,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你才可以让我一辈子痛苦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you can give me a lifetime full of misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.32,0:26:00.79,中文,,0,0,0,,没关系 我把一辈子缩短点好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, that's fine. I'm just gonna shorten the lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.79,0:26:02.13,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.13,0:26:05.36,中文,,0,0,0,,好消息 卡罗琳 我干掉了一个吸血鬼猎人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Good news, Caroline. I thwarted a vampire hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.37,0:26:08.07,中文,,0,0,0,,坏消息是 斯特凡变成吸血鬼猎人了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bad news... Stefan has become a vampire hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.07,0:26:09.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.94,0:26:13.81,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么不问他呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why don't you ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.81,0:26:18.51,中文,,0,0,0,,你做了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.72,0:26:26.49,中文,,0,0,0,,你必须停下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That is gonna have to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.49,0:26:28.75,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 你觉得这声音很讨厌\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, you think this is annoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.76,0:26:32.46,中文,,0,0,0,,那你得去听听你和邦妮每隔五分钟就会有一次的吵架\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hmm. Try listening to you and Bonnie bicker every 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.46,0:26:35.19,中文,,0,0,0,,-所以你一直在跟踪我们 -当然了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- So you've been following us. - Of course I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.20,0:26:38.20,中文,,0,0,0,,看你们俩吵架是我最接近看电视的活动了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You two are the closest thing I have a to a TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.20,0:26:40.83,中文,,0,0,0,,你们不是海岸救生队 但是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, you're no "Baywatch," But...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.83,0:26:43.67,中文,,0,0,0,,-记得海岸救生队吗 -不记得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Remember "Baywatch"? - No, I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.67,0:26:46.57,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 你必须去看看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh. Oh, man, you got to watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.57,0:26:50.07,中文,,0,0,0,,你就像救生员 很有魅力的那类\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You like lifeguards, like... Hot ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.08,0:26:51.64,中文,,0,0,0,,今天是这么多糟糕的日子以来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This has been a monumentally bad day
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.64,0:26:53.35,中文,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的一天 所以我要你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in a sea of bad days, so I'm gonna need
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.35,0:26:55.15,中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我你是谁 在这做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to know who you are, what you're doing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.15,0:26:56.35,中文,,0,0,0,,跟我有什么关系\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and how it relates to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.35,0:26:57.75,中文,,0,0,0,,否则我就撕破你的喉咙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}or I'm gonna rip your throat out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.75,0:27:00.42,中文,,0,0,0,,脾气会坏你大事的 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Temper's gonna get you in trouble, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.42,0:27:02.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你都气走邦妮多少次了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's already driven Bonnie away how many times?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.72,0:27:05.39,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 等等 我知道 十三次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, oh, oh, wait. I know. 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.39,0:27:07.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你以为我对她发脾气吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You think my temper's bad with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.53,0:27:08.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我喜欢她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.96,0:27:11.60,中文,,0,0,0,,但是你嘛 就不怎么喜欢了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You not so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.66,0:27:15.80,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧 对不起 我很认真\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok. Ok. Sorry. Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.80,0:27:17.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是对处理面对面交流\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm just kind of rusty
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.18,0:27:19.94,中文,,0,0,0,,有点生疏了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}on the face-to-face type human interactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.91,0:27:24.47,中文,,0,0,0,,回答我的问题 马上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Answers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.21,0:27:27.88,中文,,0,0,0,,也许你应该喝一口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe you should have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.88,0:27:29.98,中文,,0,0,0,,通常能使你冷静下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That usually calms you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.98,0:27:31.12,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.12,0:27:34.05,中文,,0,0,0,,然后你又会生气 之后是沮丧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Then makes you angry, then sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.05,0:27:35.95,中文,,0,0,0,,最后又会冷静下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}then calm again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.96,0:27:38.50,中文,,0,0,0,,是个奇怪的循环 听着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's a weird cycle, and look,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.50,0:27:41.80,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你真的想知道我为什么跟踪你们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}if you really want to know the reason I'm following you,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.06,0:27:46.00,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我想杀了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it's because I want to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.97,0:27:54.41,中文,,0,0,0,,马鞭草在你的体内沸腾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Vervain in your bourbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.41,0:27:56.57,中文,,0,0,0,,现在不知道是谁要遭殃了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Who didn't see that one coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.17,0:28:08.31,中文,,0,0,0,,谁会去杂货铺买露台家具\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Who buys patio furniture from a grocery store?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.31,0:28:09.54,中文,,0,0,0,,一定是有人去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, somebody must.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.55,0:28:11.71,中文,,0,0,0,,否则的话 它不会出现在这里的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Otherwise, it... it wouldn't be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.71,0:28:16.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是很了解吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but now I'm a little unfamiliar with vampires,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.55,0:28:18.14,中文,,0,0,0,,但从我收集到的资料\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but from what I've gathered,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.22,0:28:21.88,中文,,0,0,0,,把木桩插入心脏就行了 对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a stake in the heart should do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.93,0:28:25.29,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.40,0:28:28.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你一直在耍肮脏手段 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You can always fight dirty, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.90,0:28:31.93,中文,,0,0,0,,就像那次你跟邦妮玩独占游戏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Like that time you and Bonnie played monopoly
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.93,0:28:33.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你从银行里偷钱一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and you stole from the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.37,0:28:34.41,中文,,0,0,0,,一点都不酷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.77,0:28:43.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我要把你的头扭下来 -不 你不会的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I'm gonna rip your head off. - No. You're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.10,0:28:50.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道你会拿哪瓶酒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I didn't know which bottle you'd take,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.59,0:28:52.38,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我全部都加了马鞭草\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so I vervained them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.69,0:28:57.43,中文,,0,0,0,,离他远点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.43,0:28:59.53,中文,,0,0,0,,没用的人来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The useless one is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.53,0:29:01.36,中文,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.36,0:29:04.33,中文,,0,0,0,,这几个月我一直看着你试图施展魔法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've watched you try to do magic for months now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.33,0:29:06.63,中文,,0,0,0,,你要做什么 阻止我吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are you gonna do, fail at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.64,0:29:08.17,中文,,0,0,0,,真难堪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.17,0:29:10.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我为你感到难堪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm embarrassed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.63,0:29:26.49,中文,,0,0,0,,呃 哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.29,0:29:30.89,中文,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.89,0:29:33.66,中文,,0,0,0,,【咒语】\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Phesmatos.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.66,0:29:35.30,中文,,0,0,0,,火焰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Incendia.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.81,0:29:42.70,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 好了 好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok. Ok. Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.70,0:29:46.04,中文,,0,0,0,,这么快就弃械投降了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Giving up so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.04,0:29:48.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我为你感到难堪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm embarrassed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.45,0:29:55.35,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉我称呼你为世界上最讨人烦的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry I called you the most annoying person in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.35,0:29:57.62,中文,,0,0,0,,那时我还没见到他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I hadn't met him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.39,0:30:07.70,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦 那个一直都是凹的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Whoa. Was that always dented?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.70,0:30:09.33,中文,,0,0,0,,有什么关系 这只是个桶子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What the hell does it matter? It's a keg.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.33,0:30:10.80,中文,,0,0,0,,丽芙借给我的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Liv lent them to me man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.80,0:30:13.80,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 在你把你的男子气概借给丽芙的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, is that when you lent Liv your manhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.80,0:30:15.44,中文,,0,0,0,,抬上来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just lift the damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.44,0:30:17.07,中文,,0,0,0,,事实上 不用了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Actually, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.07,0:30:19.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我急需一辆空车箱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm in desperate need of an empty truck bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.78,0:30:28.72,中文,,0,0,0,,这不是你的朋友 杰 吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Isn't this your friend Jay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.72,0:30:30.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你做了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What the hell did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.49,0:30:32.86,中文,,0,0,0,,我躲过了他打算用来杀死我和斯特凡的木桩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I avoided the stake he planned to fire at Stefan and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.86,0:30:34.24,中文,,0,0,0,,木桩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stake?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.25,0:30:36.86,中文,,0,0,0,,恩 你不知道你的朋友是个吸血鬼猎人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ah. You didn't realize your friend was a vampire hunter?
