Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.54,0:30:52.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.31,0:30:57.02,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stefan!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.23,0:31:00.88,中文,,0,0,0,,别走 好吗 对不起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stop, ok? I am sorry.
