Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.32,0:31:07.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我在自欺欺人 用她来逃避现实\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was fooling myself, I was using her as an escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.26,0:31:10.02,中文,,0,0,0,,是 我知道你在想什么 卡罗琳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, I know what you think, Caroline.
