Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.56,0:31:14.49,中文,,0,0,0,,但是 杀了恩佐能让她起死回生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"But killing Enzo won't bring her back."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.50,0:31:17.86,中文,,0,0,0,,不能 但杀了他能阻止他让我想起我哥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, but it will stop him from reminding me of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.87,0:31:19.53,中文,,0,0,0,,杀了他 我就能离开这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I kill him, I can leave this place,
