Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.91,0:31:30.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是你去找埃林娜的原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's why you visited Elena,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.08,0:31:31.81,中文,,0,0,0,,你来参加派对的原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that's why you came to this party,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.81,0:31:36.42,中文,,0,0,0,,只是为了要杀恩佐 然后重新开始生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}just to kill Enzo and start over?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.66,0:31:40.30,中文,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.29,0:31:44.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.49,0:31:48.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道有你心里有个部分想念着这个地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know that a part of you misses this place
