Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.57,0:31:54.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道回到这里会让你想起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know that being back here reminds you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.13,0:31:58.07,中文,,0,0,0,,我们有多么需要你 我 有多么需要你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}how much we need you, how much... I need you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.84,0:32:03.38,中文,,0,0,0,,但如果我错了 那就走吧 离开 重新开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but if I'm wrong, then go ahead. Just go. Start over,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.38,0:32:06.65,中文,,0,0,0,,但 天啊 如果我对了呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but, God, if I'm right,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.65,0:32:09.12,中文,,0,0,0,,如果 有一小部分的你 回来这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}if just a little part of you came back
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.12,0:32:10.35,中文,,0,0,0,,是为了看看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to check on Elena,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.35,0:32:11.98,中文,,0,0,0,,痛苦不堪了四个月的埃林娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}who's had an unbearable 4 months,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.99,0:32:14.72,中文,,0,0,0,,或者是刚刚死而复生的阿拉里克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}or Alaric, who just came back from the dead,
