Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.91,0:34:24.58,中文,,0,0,0,,这意味着所有你强制催眠让人忘记的记忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Which means that every memory you compelled away
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.58,0:34:26.68,中文,,0,0,0,,都恢复了 所有 莎拉 你攻击\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}came back, so Sarah, the girl you attacked
