Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.11,0:34:58.78,中文,,0,0,0,,什么 不 不 不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What? No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.78,0:35:00.71,中文,,0,0,0,,这些是给我吃的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}These are for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.71,0:35:04.22,中文,,0,0,0,,你只有挨棍子的份\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You just get the poker.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.22,0:35:07.02,中文,,0,0,0,,-你没必要这么做 -没有吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Yeah. You don't have to do that. - No?
