Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.39,0:35:18.23,中文,,0,0,0,,重要的是你的魔力回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The important thing is that you have your magic back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.23,0:35:20.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我的方法有用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.57,0:35:22.43,中文,,0,0,0,,你不会真的以为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What, you... you didn't really think
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.43,0:35:24.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我会杀了达蒙吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'd kill Damon, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.54,0:35:28.91,中文,,0,0,0,,哈哈 这怎么有可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Heh heh. In what universe does that make sense?
