Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.98,0:35:33.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我又不是禽兽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.91,0:35:36.05,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道邦妮会出现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I knew Bonnie would show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.05,0:35:39.55,中文,,0,0,0,,她总是会回来的 十三次都是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She always comes back, all 13 times,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.55,0:35:41.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道只要刺激到位了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I knew with the right motivation
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.69,0:35:43.96,中文,,0,0,0,,她就会重获魔力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}she'd be able to access her magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.96,0:35:47.23,中文,,0,0,0,,虽然我有点担心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}although I-I did get a little worried
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.23,0:35:48.73,中文,,0,0,0,,你们吵了这么多次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}with all your bickering that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.73,0:35:51.13,中文,,0,0,0,,用达蒙的生命作威胁可能不够\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damon's life wouldn't be enough motivation,
