Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.83,0:35:56.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我想这也说明了你们之间的感情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I guess that's just how you two show your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.24,0:35:59.67,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你做了这一切就是为了让我重获魔力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you did all that just to make sure I would have my magic?
