Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.70,0:38:09.53,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, ok, ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.53,0:38:11.67,中文,,0,0,0,,卡罗琳和我会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where Caroline and I will, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.67,0:38:13.44,中文,,0,0,0,,出去在边界那里找一找\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}go out and search near the border then.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.44,0:38:15.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我会继续在镇里面找的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll keep looking in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.24,0:38:17.14,中文,,0,0,0,,有什么发现我会告诉你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll call you if I find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.95,0:38:25.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我打算在我们出去找的过程中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So I was just gonna leave my clothes here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.88,0:38:28.78,中文,,0,0,0,,把衣服放在这 如果你不介意的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}while we look, if that's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.79,0:38:30.45,中文,,0,0,0,,好啊 当然可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.45,0:38:32.42,中文,,0,0,0,,我在想 你也知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I also was thinking that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.42,0:38:33.86,中文,,0,0,0,,如果真的有吸血鬼猎人在活动的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}if there are vampire hunters on the loose
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.86,0:38:36.69,中文,,0,0,0,,独自一人住在他们地下室旁边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}then living alone right by their home base
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.69,0:38:38.86,中文,,0,0,0,,可能不是很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is probably not a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.86,0:38:42.10,中文,,0,0,0,,这是正式住下来的意思吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is this an official unpack?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.10,0:38:46.47,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我不太理解你的意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because your moving methods are just so confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.47,0:38:49.31,中文,,0,0,0,,是 这是正式住下来的意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes, this is an official unpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.31,0:38:50.57,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.57,0:38:52.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉之前对你发脾气了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sorry I got mad at you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.64,0:38:56.38,中文,,0,0,0,,有时候只是忍不住 你好像\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sometimes, it just seems like you have
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.38,0:38:58.91,中文,,0,0,0,,有可以开始新生活的秘诀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}this secret way to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.68,0:39:04.95,中文,,0,0,0,,-这是 -邦妮的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Is this... - Bonnie's?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.96,0:39:07.66,中文,,0,0,0,,是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.66,0:39:09.16,中文,,0,0,0,,就是这个了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.16,0:39:12.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你发现了我开始新生活的秘诀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You just discovered my secret to moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.53,0:39:14.93,中文,,0,0,0,,有些时候 我做不到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sometimes, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.97,0:39:21.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我想念邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I miss Bonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.37,0:39:23.47,中文,,0,0,0,,想念神秘瀑布镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I miss Mystic Falls,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.47,0:39:25.41,中文,,0,0,0,,想念过去的一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I miss our old life,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.41,0:39:29.01,中文,,0,0,0,,-想念 -斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I miss... - Stefan?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.02,0:39:36.52,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 想念斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. I miss Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.52,0:39:38.99,中文,,0,0,0,,卡罗琳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Caroline...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.72,0:39:42.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你和斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You and Stefan...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.96,0:39:46.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你是不是喜欢他还是怎样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you have feelings for him or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.60,0:39:56.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我想我可能是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, I think maybe I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.01,0:40:07.05,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们应该出发了 去找那个女生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, we should go ahead and find that girl
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.05,0:40:08.82,中文,,0,0,0,,得赶在她摆脱我们之前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}before she outs us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.09,0:40:19.43,中文,,0,0,0,,难过的一晚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rough night?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.43,0:40:23.33,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 这不是一块蛋糕就能弥补的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ahh. Nothing a piece of pie can't fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.33,0:40:25.57,中文,,0,0,0,,有人来帮忙倒酒水我感激不尽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Service would be lovely, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.57,0:40:27.14,中文,,0,0,0,,是我的错 抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My fault. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.14,0:40:30.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我叫大家回去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I sent everyone home for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.04,0:40:34.27,中文,,0,0,0,,不能再让你杀酒保了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can't have you killing any more of the wait staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.28,0:40:35.78,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Unh!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.35,0:40:42.92,中文,,0,0,0,,喝血的时候小心点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Consider being more discreet when you feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.92,0:40:45.19,中文,,0,0,0,,因为你不知道有谁会看着你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You never know whose eyes are watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.19,0:40:47.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我相信这个通常会起作用 是不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I bet this normally works, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.82,0:40:50.02,中文,,0,0,0,,能让吸血鬼昏迷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Knocks vampires right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.03,0:40:54.03,中文,,0,0,0,,看到了吗 我和普通的吸血鬼不一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}See, I'm a bit different than a normal vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.03,0:40:57.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我可以抵抗马鞭草的效用 不是很久\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can fight the vervain, not for long, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.53,0:41:01.20,中文,,0,0,0,,够时间解决你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Long enough to take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.61,0:41:12.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我在你们当中的一人身上找到这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I found this on one of your guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.18,0:41:14.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我相信是被他杀了的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think he killed him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.92,0:41:17.89,中文,,0,0,0,,-你是谁 -斯特凡 萨瓦托尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Who are you? - Stefan Salvatore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.89,0:41:21.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你和我有相似之处\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You and I have something in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.12,0:41:25.09,中文,,0,0,0,,都是来自创始人家族 谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}One of the founding families. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.46,0:41:31.40,中文,,0,0,0,,其实 如果你不介意的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Actually... If you don't mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.40,0:41:35.07,中文,,0,0,0,,我有偏好的杀死他们的方式\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have my own way I like them to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.44,0:41:44.68,中文,,0,0,0,,让他们死得痛苦点就行了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just make sure it's painful.
